  +nxml-gentoo-schemas-20080301.ebuild:
  Version bump, updates book.rnc.

  29 Feb 2008; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org>
  files/60nxml-gentoo-schemas-gentoo.el:
  Add "eval-after-load" in site-init file, so that it works with builtin
  nxml-mode in Emacs 23, too.

